{"tid":2060623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港700萬人已經獨立左, 林鄭/共狗/兩辦/黑警講乜做乜都WFC","createTime":"2020-06-11T19:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T07:45:27.000Z","uid":123774,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6843aefa2fc73d42543b01948646459c039ea11d","tid":2060623,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T19:54:32.000Z","msg":"話乜非法集會<br />\n睬你都多撚餘照出<br />\n以前有制度批不反<br />\n班官同黑警玩爛咗個制度之後<br />\n依家佢仲難攪 全世界當佢9噏<br />\n何時何地都照集合<br />\n和你非都慣咗帶身分證再袋定$2000行街<br />\n<br />\n攪國歌法 給果:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJgHdKC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJgHdKC.jpg&h=1bbdf979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出埋黨媒大力抨擊黃色經濟圈<br />\n點知越講越多人分顏色<br />\n<br />\n之前兩辦出黎出口術<br />\n結果又係冇人理佢哋<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄隻冚家剷出黎9up<br />\nD人都係當佢小丑咁睇冇人理<br />\n<br />\n依家係佢哋做乜講乜都被你視<br />\n一個政權認受性係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>零</strong></span></span><br />\n共狗都真係幾好野先可以幫700萬香港人獨立<br />\n台灣鄧係越走越遠 鄧小平真係死唔眼閉"},{"pid":"ca0993d4002ff098d02bab94760bc4fe586641d6","tid":2060623,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T19:56:00.000Z","msg":"依家仲要咁多國家開行turno講接收香港難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bff6a090068de06baa934739e41d57ed811f0b","tid":2060623,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T20:00:18.000Z","msg":"香港人點睇一班高官黑警?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MuphM9J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMuphM9J.jpg&h=9bf02ed0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b04b2d1ba798d8f0971161c8fe0ac454f66ce351","tid":2060623,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T21:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fNbTkU5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfNbTkU5.gif&h=dff99682&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e42ec1edb292f7f3cc24020c9cda79b19fcfc3f"